<h2 id="guy-clarks-telling-of-the-tale">Guy Clark‚Äôs telling of the tale</h2>

<p>Here‚Äôs a short video of Guy Clark telling the story behind this song ‚Äì¬†i.e., him and Townes Van Zandt were drinking &amp; acting afool, which lead to Clark‚Äôs wife storming out of the house. Where, chance would have it, a friend with a Polaroid camera was waiting. In this video he also performs the song. It‚Äôs absolutely not as sharp as the official album cut, but it‚Äôs still valuable in that it shows how a very stripped back, solo, and minimal performance of this song can still work. Enjoy!</p>

